---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Custom AI Software Development — Zero Fluff"
  description="Custom AI software development for small businesses in Devon and the South West UK. We build bespoke AI-powered tools, integrate AI into your existing systems, and create custom automation workflows."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">CUSTOM AI SOFTWARE DEVELOPMENT</span>
      <h1>Bespoke AI software,<br>built around your business</h1>
      <p>Off-the-shelf tools only get you so far. When you need something that fits exactly how your business works, we build it — AI-powered software, custom integrations, and automation designed for the way you actually operate.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <section class="intro-section">
    <div class="intro-inner">
      <p>Most businesses don't need another generic SaaS subscription. They need software that does the specific thing they do, the way they do it — with AI quietly doing the heavy lifting underneath. That's what we build. With 30 years of software experience behind us and modern AI tooling in front, we ship custom AI software that's genuinely useful, not just impressive in a demo. We work with businesses across Devon and the wider South West UK, as well as clients further afield.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE BUILD -->
  <section class="services-detail">
    <article class="service-row">
      <div class="service-img service-img-1"></div>
      <div class="service-text">
        <span class="service-tag-label">BESPOKE TOOLS</span>
        <h2>AI-powered tools built for you</h2>
        <p>Have a process that no existing product handles properly? We design and build custom AI tools from scratch — internal dashboards, document processors, customer-facing apps, AI assistants trained on your own knowledge. You own it, it does exactly what you need, and it grows with you.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Bespoke web apps and internal tools</li>
          <li>AI assistants trained on your data and documents</li>
          <li>Document and data processing pipelines</li>
          <li>Built on Claude, ChatGPT and the right model for the job</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-red">Discuss your idea →</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="service-row service-row-reverse">
      <div class="service-img service-img-2"></div>
      <div class="service-text">
        <span class="service-tag-label">INTEGRATION</span>
        <h2>AI built into your existing systems</h2>
        <p>You don't have to rip out what already works. We integrate AI into the tools and systems you already use — your CRM, your website, your spreadsheets, your line-of-business software. The AI slots in where it adds value, and your team carries on working the way they're used to. See how we <a href="/case-studies/fandemiq" class="inline-link">helped FANDEMiQ understand an 8-year-old platform</a> and add AI to a live product.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>AI features added to existing products</li>
          <li>Integrations with CRMs, APIs and databases</li>
          <li>Connecting AI to the tools your team already uses</li>
          <li>Migrations and modernisation of older systems</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-red">Talk integrations →</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="service-row">
      <div class="service-img service-img-3"></div>
      <div class="service-text">
        <span class="service-tag-label">WORKFLOWS</span>
        <h2>Custom automation workflows</h2>
        <p>When a one-size-fits-all automation tool isn't enough, we build custom workflows that chain AI, your data and your systems together — handling the multi-step, judgement-heavy processes that usually eat a person's whole afternoon. See how we built <a href="/case-studies/house-builder-report-generation" class="inline-link">automated report generation for a house builder</a>.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Multi-step AI workflows using N8N and custom code</li>
          <li>Automated reporting, summarising and data entry</li>
          <li>Triggered actions across multiple systems</li>
          <li>Monitoring so you know it's working</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-red">Get a Quote →</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
  <section class="who-section">
    <div class="who-inner">
      <span class="section-label">IS THIS YOU?</span>
      <h2>Custom AI software makes sense when…</h2>
      <div class="who-grid">
        <div class="who-card">
          <p>You've outgrown spreadsheets and off-the-shelf tools, but a full software team is overkill.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="who-card">
          <p>You have a repetitive, rules-and-judgement process that no existing product handles well.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="who-card">
          <p>You want AI in your product or operations, but need someone who'll actually build and ship it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="who-card">
          <p>You've got data sitting unused that could be answering questions or making decisions for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EXPLORE MORE -->
  <section class="services-explore">
    <div class="services-explore-inner">
      <span class="section-label">EXPLORE MORE</span>
      <h2>See it in practice</h2>
      <div class="explore-grid">
        <a href="/case-studies" class="explore-card">
          <h3>Case studies →</h3>
          <p>Real custom AI builds for real businesses — see the work and the results.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/services" class="explore-card">
          <h3>All services →</h3>
          <p>From a two-hour AI Quick Start to ongoing support — see the full range.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/ai-automation-devon" class="explore-card">
          <h3>AI for Devon businesses →</h3>
          <p>How we help businesses across Devon put AI and automation to work.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/ai-consultancy-south-west" class="explore-card">
          <h3>AI consultancy in the South West →</h3>
          <p>Practical AI consultancy for businesses across the South West UK.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="services-cta">
    <div class="services-cta-content">
      <h2>Got something in mind?</h2>
      <p>Book a free 20-minute chat. Tell me what you're trying to build — I'll tell you straight whether AI is the right tool, and how I'd approach it.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-red cta-btn-lg">Book a free AI chat →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* PAGE HERO */
  .page-hero {
    min-height: 520px;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .page-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 80px;
    max-width: 860px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FF3B30;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .page-hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }
  .page-hero-content p {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* INTRO */
  .intro-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 80px;
  }
  .intro-inner {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .intro-inner p {
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* SERVICES DETAIL */
  .services-detail {
    padding: 0 80px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }
  .service-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 60px 0;
  }
  .service-row:first-child {
    padding-top: 60px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .service-row-reverse .service-img { order: 2; }
  .service-row-reverse .service-text { order: 1; }
  .service-img {
    height: 400px;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .service-img::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .service-img-1 { background-image: url('/images/service-projects.png'); }
  .service-img-1::after { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0533, #0a1628); }
  .service-img-2 { background-image: url('/images/service-automation.png'); }
  .service-img-2::after { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #081a1a, #0a1a0d); }
  .service-img-3 { background-image: url('/images/service-quickstart.png'); }
  .service-img-3::after { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d1408, #1a0a0a); }
  .service-text {
    padding: 0 60px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .service-tag-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #FF3B30;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .service-text h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .service-text > p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .service-text ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .service-text li {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .service-text li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #FF3B30;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .inline-link {
    color: #FF3B30;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 59, 48, 0.4);
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .inline-link:hover { border-bottom-color: #FF3B30; }
  .btn-red {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #FF3B30;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    text-decoration: none;
    align-self: flex-start;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-red:hover { opacity: 0.85; color: #fff; }

  /* WHO IT'S FOR */
  .who-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 80px;
  }
  .who-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FF3B30;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .who-inner > h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .who-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .who-card {
    padding: 28px;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 3px solid #FF3B30;
  }
  .who-card p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* EXPLORE MORE */
  .services-explore {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 80px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .services-explore-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .services-explore-inner > h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .explore-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .explore-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 28px;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .explore-card:hover {
    border-color: #FF3B30;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .explore-card h3 {
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }
  .explore-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .services-cta {
    min-height: 300px;
    background: #000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .services-cta-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 80px;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .services-cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }
  .services-cta-content p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #ccc;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .cta-btn-lg {
    font-size: 18px;
    padding: 20px 48px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero-content { padding: 0 24px; }
    .page-hero-content h1 { font-size: 38px; }
    .intro-section { padding: 60px 24px; }
    .intro-inner p { font-size: 19px; }
    .services-detail { padding: 0 24px; }
    .service-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 40px 0; }
    .service-row-reverse .service-img { order: 0; }
    .service-row-reverse .service-text { order: 0; }
    .service-text { padding: 32px 0 0; }
    .who-section { padding: 60px 24px; }
    .who-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .services-explore { padding: 60px 24px; }
    .explore-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .services-cta-content { padding: 40px 24px; }
    .services-cta-content h2 { font-size: 36px; }
  }
</style>
